'''Brian George''' (July [[1952]]) is an Israeli born actor. He voiced characters in several [[J.R.R. Tolkien|Tolkien]]-related [[:Category:Video games|video games]].

==Roles==
* [[2009]] - ''[[The Lord of the Rings: Conquest]]'' - [[Théoden]] / Elven Officer #2 / Old Male Hobbit
* [[2006]] - ''[[The Lord of the Rings: The Battle for Middle-earth II]]'' - [[Théoden]]
* [[2003]] - ''[[The Hobbit (2003 video game)|The Hobbit]]'' - Additional voices
